      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like shine, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface marks expected of a carefully driven car. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at regular intervals. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, ensuring the brakes and tires have plenty of life left. It is a turn-key example ready for its next long-term owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
